title: Verify Login Successfully
steps_actions:
1. Go to URL https://katalon-demo-cura.herokuapp.com/
2. Click The Three Lines button in the top right corner
3. Click Log in button
4. Input Valid Username
5. Input Valid Password
6. Click Log in button
steps_result:
1. Successfully redirect to CURA Health Service page
2. Appear the menu
3. Redirect to Log in page
4. Username Appear
5. Password Appear
6. Success Logged in

title: Verify Login Failed (Invalid Password)
postconditions: Showing Error Message and Redirect back to Log in page
steps_actions:
1. Go to URL https://katalon-demo-cura.herokuapp.com/
2. Click The Three Lines button in the top right corner
3. Click Log in button
4. Input Valid Username
5. Input WRONG Password
6. Click Log in button
steps_result:
1. Successfully redirect to CURA Health Service page
2. Appear the menu
3. Redirect to Log in page
4. Username Appear
5. Password Appear
6. Failed Log in

title: Verify Log out Successfully
steps_actions:
1. Click The Three Lines button in the top right corner
2. Click Log out button
steps_result:
1. Appear the menu
2. Success Logged out

title: Verify Book Appoinment
steps_actions:
1. Click Facility option and select
2. Select Healthcare Program
3. Click Visit Date and select
4. Write Comment
5. Click Book Appointment button
steps_result:
1. Facility option appear
2. Healthcare Program selected
3. Visit Date Appear
4. Comment Appear
5. Success Book Appointment
steps_data:
1. Tokyo CURA Healthcare Center
2. Medicare
3. 31/01/2023
4. I want to book appointment
5.
